o run a live service right away. I've gotten a better sense of why fallback UIs, exception handling, and error monitoring are important."), mdx("p", null, "One of the most important assets I've gained from this bumpy ride is the confidence that \"I can learn and grow anywhere\"."), mdx("p", null, "Of course, it's slow and sometimes limiting for a junior to learn on their own in an early startup, so you need a good team and good seniors to make the growth graph steep."), mdx("p", null, "However, I would say that my time at Moye was valuable in that it confirmed my ability to develop myself even in extreme situations where I was chased by milestones without enough team members, including seniors, and was able to make some contributions to the team and the company."), mdx("h1", {
